        {
            "title": "北角海璇4房特色戶2億沽 呎價84,282元創港島東新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Rc9XdsV5wUvZdHqP0lmO8Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/28hse_com_210/f848cc03668b305c4ca6b71cdaf0af6e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
